Introduction

Na Jae Min, also known as Jaemin, is a member of the boy group NCT. On August 24, 2016, Jaemin debuted as a member of its sub-unit NCT Dream.

Besides being a singer, Jaemin also engages in various entertainment activities. In 2018, he joined the cast of tvN's My English Teen 100 Hours Season 2, an educational variety show where cast members study English intensively before being sent abroad to test their real-life English skills. Moreover, Jaemin made his acting debut in JTBC's short web drama Method to Hate You, which was based on a popular webtoon of the same name.
